videos.description: South Dakota State's Macy Miller talks about finally beating South Dakota in the Summit League Championship after falling to them twice in the regular season.
videos.headline: Miller leads Jackrabbits back to NCAA Tournament

tracking.trackingName: COM_ESPNW Interview (Miller leads Jackrabbits back to NCAA Tournament) 2016/03/08 ESHEET

videos.description: South Dakota State's Macy Miller's 18 points led the way over South Dakota as the Jackrabbits return to the NCAA Tournament for the seventh time in eight years.
videos.headline: South Dakota St. tops South Dakota in Summit League final
